On Escalation Ticket # 00427245 the new comment has been added: Marius Ghiurcau:

@WaitingOnEngineer

Since the issue is only reproducing on one machine, can the customer tell us if there is any particular setup on that machine? Any apps that could interfere with the EPP client? (such as AVs, VPNs) 
I saw they have some Cisco products installed, is the issue reproducing when CISCO is disabled/uninstalled? Did they test on multiple browsers (Safari, Firefox), or only Chrome? Please gather more info for us and new tests should be made with this build: 

\192.168.14.5Publicgroups_daily_buildsCoSoSys2024-builds2024_11_29EppMac_v3.0.4.1006

It is the RC for 5941 and contains some improvements related to DPI. 

@Cristian-Alexandru Halmajan @Krzysztof Staszalek can you please help us with a download link? Thanks

On Escalation Ticket # 00427245 the new comment has been added: Hi Team,

The update from our partner on this case is as follows:

"The status of this case is follow:
If the Intercept VPN traffic is ON - customer have issues with Google Meet, that is why they disabled this option.
But, without the Intercept VPN traffic option, there is internet speed issue occurs on several computers.
And unfortunately, customer cannot enable Intercept VPN traffic there because of Google meet issue.
So, if we will fix the issue with Google meet (#429094) this issue should be fixed as well."

The above is referring to ADO: https://dev.azure.com/NetwrixCorporation/CoSoSys-EPP/_workitems/edit/367786

The internet speed decrease issue is an Apple bug and there is nothing that we can do about it. So the customer will have to enable Intercept VPN traffic. We will have to resume investigations and find solutions for the customer from intercept VPN enabled.

''Thank you for the update.
Customer is trying to enable intercept VPN traffic to all possible computers, but for some of them issue with Google meet occurs.
Ticket number: #00429094 Issues with Google meet on macOS

Is there some workaround that could be done in the meantime for this tow work with Google Meet while intercept VPN is enabled?
Please let us know.
